    "Validation is crucial to confirm the therapeutic relevance of these targets.",
    "To this end, an array of molecular techniques are used for gene and protein-level verification, while cell-based assays further substantiate the biological significance of the targets in a more complex environment.",
    "The introduction of AI in this phase has accelerated the processing of large datasets, speeding up target validation.",
    "After validating drug targets, the subsequent phase in drug discovery is identifying \"hits,\" molecules that affect the activity of the target.",
    "This phase emphasizes exploring a diverse range of molecular structures, as some may show initial activity but prove challenging to optimize."
